<plot>Megan comes home to join her Jewish family for Shabbat dinner with an important announcement: she's a lesbian and she's engaged to her girlfriend, Christina. But her well-intentioned family has already planned a celebration for her; they think she's engaged to her best friend, Markus. As Megan puts off breaking the news to her family, things quickly spiral out of control. Who knew telling the truth could be so complicated?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?519991</url></doc>
